  <brief_title>Study of ARO-HBV in Normal Adult Volunteers and Patients With Hepatitis B Virus (HBV)</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase 1/2a Single Dose-Escalating Study to Evaluate the Safety, Tolerability and Pharmacokinetic Effects of ARO-HBV in Normal Adult Volunteers and Multiple Escalating Doses Evaluating Safety, Tolerability and Pharmacodynamic Effects in HBV Patients</official_title>
